»CL9:----------------------> »CL8:rules

           »CL1: *»CL7: No drugs or alcohol of any kind will be
              accepted. Intoxicated people will be
              thrown out and handed over to the police
           »CL1: *»CL7: No smoking inside the party-halls
           »CL1: *»CL7: No violence including people / inventory
              [ no self destructing ]
           »CL1: *»CL7: No extraterrestial beings / aliens
           »CL1: *»CL7: No home appliances [ microwave ovens /
              fridges / vacuum cleaners etc ]
           »CL1: *»CL7: No hacking / phreaking / anarchy
           »CL1: *»CL7: No network spoofing
           »CL1: *»CL7: No stealing
           »CL1: *»CL7: No fireworks
           »CL1: *»CL7: No pets [ that includes tamagotchies =) ]
           »CL1: *»CL7: No barbeque inside the party-halls
           »CL1: *»CL7: No trippin'
           »CL1: *»CL7: No cheating
           »CL1: *»CL7: No ENOURMOUS LOUD STEREO SPEAKERS!




















           »CL1: *»CL7: No loff-throwing
           »CL1: *»CL7: No spacerom-selling
           »CL1: *»CL7: No rope-climbing
           »CL1: *»CL7: No writing on the walls / doors / whatever
           »CL1: *»CL7: No fire [ i.e. no burning doors /
              plastic containers ]
           »CL1: *»CL7: No lazers [ includes phazers and rifles ]
           »CL1: *»CL7: No smurfehits
           »CL1: *»CL7: No use of fire-exstinguishers [ except to
              actually extinguish a fire ]
           »CL1: *»CL7: No ugly annoying girl-voice announcing
              "Bernt-gunnar, mammaen og pappaen din
              venter i informasjonen"



























              In addition to these rules, "norwegian
              laws are enabled and active" during the
              party. Any violation(s) to these rules
              and / or the norwegian laws may cause
              police involvement. The organizers will
              not be responsible for any damage to
              you, your computer or the damage you may
              cause. The organizers will also not be
              responsible for any computer piracy,
              which will not be accepted and will
              hopefully not occur. Some of our
              sponsors will stop by, so for gods sake,
              behave yourselves =)



























